      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776685136072,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Block Editing - Page\n- the whole page component is a combination of blocks.\n- type to create new block by default text-block\n- keyboard `enter` = new block, `backspace` = delete empty\n- slash / command to change block type\n- drag handlers to reorder blocks",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Block Editing - Page\n- the whole page component is a combination of blocks.\n- type to create new block by default text-block\n- keyboard `enter` = new block, `backspace` = delete empty\n- slash / command to change block type\n- drag handlers to reorder blocks",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "PnoTkf_-P0urt6M2yqzm1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -210.64285714285688,
      "y": 674.0595238095239,
      "width": 586.3757934570312,
      "height": 350,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "sH88ioil7p4NJ9ckbWRCq",
      "index": "aa",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 207288108,
      "version": 713,
      "versionNonce": 2047333548,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776685136072,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Block Types (V1) - \n- Paragraph, Heading 1/2/3\n- Code blocks (with language lable)\n- Quote and horizontal divider block\n- Todo checkboxes \n\n@NOTE: default block type = text block\nin case of checkboxes and other type of\nlists the current block type should persist.\nApart from headings, dividers etc.  ",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Block Types (V1) - \n- Paragraph, Heading 1/2/3\n- Code blocks (with language lable)\n- Quote and horizontal divider block\n- Todo checkboxes \n\n@NOTE: default block type = text block\nin case of checkboxes and other type of\nlists the current block type should persist.\nApart from headings, dividers etc.  ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "SthW9f1ciNGo6Bo0x6p5m",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 472.7380952380961,
      "y": 737.2976190476194,
      "width": 631.8478393554688,
      "height": 280,
      "angle": 0,
