      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Component Name: \nSidebar.tsx\n\nUI Design: \nDock like, maybe there will be an auto-hide feature\n\nFunctionality: \nShows a list of pages available.\nAllows to open pages, and create new ones.\n\nReads pageSlice, dispatches createPage/setActivePage. \nNeed to add a delete option too. ",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Component Name: \nSidebar.tsx\n\nUI Design: \nDock like, maybe there will be an auto-hide feature\n\nFunctionality: \nShows a list of pages available.\nAllows to open pages, and create new ones.\n\nReads pageSlice, dispatches createPage/setActivePage. \nNeed to add a delete option too. ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
