      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "c. SlashMenu.tsx\n\nFloating command pallet. Opens on '/' , filters on subsequent keys, closes on Escape or selection.",
